Introduction

Choi Seung Cheol, better known by his stage name S.Coups, is a South Korean rapper, singer, dancer, songwriter and composer under Pledis Entertainment. He is the leader, lead rapper and sub vocalist of the boy group SEVENTEEN. S.coups is also the leader of the group's Hip Hop unit SVT HIPHOP Team.

S.Coups debuted as the leader of SEVENTEEN on May 26, 2015 with their first mini album "17 Carat".
